room_title: Escape room "Huxley 1 VR" by Epic Team Adventures in Seattle
room_description: 3007 AD: The world, as you know it, is gone. Mankind was replaced by machines. What was once green, is now destroyed. You are the last, remaining survivors, with one mission: to help HUXLEY. With your first step into the virtual reality, you have 44 minutes to reverse the apocalypse. Everything you need to succeed can be found within your team: Adrenaline, a fighting spirit and a desire to win.
